fields.translation: This young lady's surname is li.
You are a teacher.
Hello teacher!
You are a student.
Miss li is a student.
I am not a teacher.
I am a teacher.

fields.pinyin: Qǐng wèn nǐ shì lǐ xiǎo jiě ma?
fields.translation: Are you miss li, please?
Please come to china.

fields.chinese: 李小姐问我你是老师吗。
fields.pinyin: Lǐ xiǎo jiě wèn wǒ nǐ shì lǎo shī ma.
fields.translation: Miss li asks me if you are a teacher.

fields.pinyin: Qǐng wèn nǐ shì lǐ xiǎo jiě ma
fields.translation: Are you miss li, please?
I’m a student.
My surname is wang.
You are a student.
My family name is li. how about you?
What's your name?
What's the young lady's surname please?

fields.pinyin: Wǒ de míngzì shì lǐ yǒu.
fields.translation: My name is li you.
What's your name?
Are you mr. li?
My husband's surname is li.

fields.pinyin: Nǐ shì lǐ xiān shēng ma
fields.translation: Are you mr. li?
I‘m li you.

fields.pinyin: Wǒ de míngzì shì lǐ yǒu
fields.translation: My name is li you.
I'm wang peng.

fields.pinyin: Wǒ de míngzì shì wáng péng.
fields.translation: My name is wang peng.

fields.pinyin: Nǐ shì lǐ xiǎo jiě ma
fields.translation: Are you miss wang?
He's chinese.
Are you american?

fields.chinese: 他是美国人，她也是美国人。
fields.pinyin: Tā shì měiguó rén, tā yěshì měiguó rén.
fields.translation: He is american, and she is also american.
I come from beijing.
I am not from new york.

fields.chinese: 你没有什么工作经验，先找个地方实习一下。
fields.pinyin: Nǐ méiyǒu shénme gōngzuò jīngyàn, xiān zhǎo ge dìfāng shíxí yí xià.
fields.translation: You don't have a lot of working experience; you could find a place to intern first.

fields.chinese: 他已经学了三年化学了。
fields.pinyin: Tā yǐjīng xué le sān nián huàxué le.
fields.translation: He's been studying chemistry for three years.

fields.chinese: 我想学化学专业，将来好找工作。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng xué huàxué zhuānyè, jiānglái hǎo zhǎo gōngzuò.
fields.translation: I'd like to major in chemistry so that i can get a job easily.

fields.chinese: 大家决定开一个舞会来给他过生日。
fields.pinyin: Dàjiā juédìng kāi yīgè wǔhuì lái gěi tā guò shēngrì.
fields.translation: Everybody decided to throw a dance party to celebrate his birthday.

fields.chinese: 你对丽莎的决定有什么看法?
fields.pinyin: Nǐ duì lìshā de juédìng yǒu shénme kànfǎ?
fields.translation: What do you think of lisa's decision?

fields.chinese: 这本书对世界经济的介绍最清楚不过了。
fields.pinyin: Zhè běn shū duì shìjiè jīngjì de jièshào zuì qīngchǔ búguòle.
fields.translation: This book's presentation of the world economy surpasses all others in its clarity.

fields.chinese: 中国西边是高原, 那儿有世界上最高的山。
fields.pinyin: Zhōngguó xī biān shì gāoyuán, nà'er yǒu shìjiè shàng zuìgāo de shān.
fields.translation: In the western part of china there are plateaus. there you'll find the world's tallest mountain.

fields.chinese: 我们先讨论去不去,至于什么时候去,以后再说。
fields.pinyin: Wǒmen xiān tǎolùn qù bù qù, zhìyú shénme shíhòu qù, yǐhòu zàishuō.
fields.translation: Let's first discuss whether we'll go or not. as for when to go, we'll talk about that later.

fields.chinese: 这个问题我们讨论来讨论去,最后还是没有办法解决。
fields.pinyin: Zhège wèntí wǒmen tǎolùn lái tǎolùn qù, zuìhòu háishì méiyǒu bànfǎ jiějué.
fields.translation: We discussed this problem again and again. in the end we still couldn't find a way to solve it.

fields.chinese: 我一直以为整天跟数字打交道没什么意思,实际上挺好玩儿的。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ yīzhí yǐwéi zhěngtiān gēn shùzì dǎjiāodào méishénme yìsi, shíjìshang tǐng hǎowán'er de.
fields.translation: I always had a misconception that it was boring to handle numbers and figures all day long. in fact, it's quite fun.

fields.chinese: 我妈妈在银行工作,天天跟钱和数字打交道。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ māmā zài yínháng gōngzuò, tiāntiān gēn qián hé shùzì dǎjiāodào.
fields.translation: My mom works at a bank. she deals with money and numbers every day.

fields.chinese: 这个学期已经过了一半,马上又得选下学期的课了,张天明希望下个学期能轻松点儿。
fields.pinyin: Zhè ge xuéqī yǐjīng guò le yí bàn, mǎshàng yòu děi xuǎn xià xuéqī de kè le, zhāng tiānmíng xīwàng xià ge xuéqī néng qīngsōng diǎnr.
fields.translation: This semester is half over. soon he'll have to choose next semester's classes. zhang tianming hopes that he can relax a bit more next semester.

fields.chinese: 可是现在,每次上中文课我就想,要是我小时候父母就让我学中文,我现在就轻松多了。
fields.pinyin: Kěshì xiànzài, měi cì shàng zhōngwén kè wǒ jiù xiǎng, yàoshi wǒ xiǎoshíhou fùmǔ jiù ràng wǒ xué zhōngwén, wǒ xiànzài jiù qīngsōng duō le.
fields.translation: But now every time i'm in my chinese class i wish that my parents had made me learn chinese when i was a child. i would have a much easier time.

fields.pinyin: Zhāng jiàoshòu xiě wénzhāng xiě lèile.
fields.translation: Professor zhang was tired from writing articles.

fields.chinese: 老教授慢慢地走进了教室。
fields.pinyin: Lǎo jiàoshòu mànman de zǒu jìnle jiàoshì.
fields.translation: The old professor slowly walked into the classroom.

fields.chinese: 历史课我选了一门了, 还得选一门。
fields.pinyin: Lìshǐ kè wǒ xuǎnle yīmén le, hái děi xuǎn yī mén.
fields.translation: I've already taken one history class. i have to take one more.

fields.chinese: 张天明这个学期选了四门课:世界历史、电脑、政治学和中文。
fields.pinyin: Zhāng tiānmíng zhè ge xuéqī xuǎn le sì mén kè: shìjiè lìshǐ, diànnǎo, zhèngzhìxué hé zhōngwén.
fields.translation: Zhang tianming is taking four courses this semester: world history, computer science, political science, and chinese.

fields.chinese: 妈妈叫我学经济, 我想来想去还是选了电脑。
fields.pinyin: Māmā jiào wǒ xué jīngjì, wǒ xiǎnglái xiǎngqù háishì xuǎn le diànnǎo.
fields.translation: My mother wanted me to study economics. after thinking it over and over, i decided to study computer [science].

fields.chinese: 今年经济很糟糕,我一直找不到工作,这对我的压力很大。
fields.pinyin: Jīnnián jīngjì hěn zāogāo, wǒ yīzhí zhǎobúdào gōngzuò, zhè duì wǒ de yālì hěn dà.
fields.translation: The economy is doing really badly this year. i can't find a job and this puts a lot of pressure on me.

fields.chinese: 外面有人叫我，我开门一看，是送信的。
fields.pinyin: Wàimiàn yǒurén jiào wǒ, wǒ kāi mén yī kàn, shì sòngxìn de.
fields.translation: There was someone shouting my name outside. i opened the door and took a look, and it was the letter carrier.

fields.chinese: 下个学期我打算选三门课。
fields.pinyin: Xià gè xuéqī wǒ dǎsuàn xuǎn sān mén kè.
fields.translation: I plan to take three courses next semester.

fields.chinese: 下学期的课你选好了吗?
fields.pinyin: Xià xuéqī de kè nǐ xuǎn hǎole ma?
fields.translation: Have you finished selecting classes for next semester?

fields.chinese: 下个学期我打算选三门课。
fields.pinyin: Xià gè xuéqī wǒ dǎsuàn xuǎn sān mén kè.
fields.translation: I plan to take three courses next semester.

fields.chinese: 我哥哥经常丢三拉四的,我看有一天会把自已丢了。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ gēgē jīngcháng diūsānlāsì de, wǒ kàn yǒuyītiān huì bǎ zìyǐ diūle.
fields.translation: My older brother is such a scatterbrain. i wouldn't be surprised if he forgot who he is one day.

fields.chinese: 学外语得经常听录音、念课文,这样才能提高听和说的水平。
fields.pinyin: Xué wàiyǔ děi jīngcháng tīng lùyīn, niàn kèwén, zhèyàng cáinéng tígāo tīng hé shuō de shuǐpíng.
fields.translation: To learn a foreign language you have to listen to the audio recordings and read the lessons aloud frequently. this is the only way to improve your listening and speaking abilities.

fields.pinyin: Zhāng jiàoshòu xiě wénzhāng xiě lèi le.
fields.translation: Professor zhang was tired from writing articles.

fields.chinese: 我要写一篇文章,查一 些资料。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ yào xiě yì piān wénzhāng, chá yì xiē zīliào.
fields.translation: I have to write an article. i needed to look up some information.

fields.chinese: 今天太热，我真的受不了。
fields.pinyin: Jīntiān tài rè, wǒ zhēn de shòu bu liǎo.
fields.translation: It's so hot today. i truly can't take it.

fields.chinese: 我的同屋每天夜里两三点钟才睡觉，我真受不了。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ de tóngwū měitiān yèlǐ liǎng sān diǎn zhōng cái shuìjiào, wǒ zhēn shòu bu liǎo.
fields.translation: My roommate doesn't go to bed until two or three in the morning. i can't stand it.

fields.chinese: 她今天下午又要去见指导教授了。
fields.pinyin: Tā jīntiān xiàwǔ yòu yào qù jiàn zhǐdǎo jiàoshòu le.
fields.translation: She's going to see her advisor again this afternoon.

fields.chinese: 你这个建议真不错, 我看我也不必去找指导教授了,就听你的“指导”吧 !
fields.pinyin: Nǐ zhè ge jiànyì zhēn búcuò, wǒ kàn wǒ yě búbì qù zhǎo zhǐdǎo jiàoshòu le, jiù tīng nǐ de “zhǐdǎo” ba!
fields.translation: That's a good suggestion. it seems like i don't need to see my advisor. i can listen to your advice!

fields.chinese: 这一天下午,他在篮球场上正好碰见大四的李哲,就一边和李哲打球,一 边聊了起来。
fields.pinyin: Zhè yì tiān xiàwǔ, tā zài lánqiú chǎng shang zhènghǎo pèng jiàn dà sì de lǐ zhé, jiù yì biān hé lǐ zhé dǎ qiú, yì biān liáo le qi lai.
fields.translation: This afternoon he happens to run into li zhe on the basketball court, so he begins to chat with li zhe while they play basketball.

fields.chinese: 他是在中国出生,在中国长大的,肯定会说中文。
fields.pinyin: Tā shì zài zhōngguó chūshēng, zài zhōngguó zhǎng dà de, kěndìng huì shuō zhōngwén.
fields.translation: He was born and raised in china. he most certainly can speak chinese.

fields.chinese: 你没有什么工作经验, 先找个地方实习一下, 对将来找工作肯定有好处。
fields.pinyin: Nǐ méiyǒu shénme gōngzuò jīngyàn, xiān zhǎo ge dìfāng shíxí yí xià, duì jiānglái zhǎo gōngzuò kěndìng yǒu hǎochù.
fields.translation: You don't have a lot of working experience; you could find a place to intern first. it'll be good when you look for a job.

fields.chinese: 我们先讨论去不去,至于什么时候去,以后再说。
fields.pinyin: Wǒmen xiān tǎolùn qù bù qù, zhìyú shénme shíhòu qù, yǐhòu zàishuō.
fields.translation: Let's first discuss whether we'll go or not. as for when to go, we'll talk about that later.

fields.chinese: 我喜欢吃广东菜,至于我太太,她喜欢吃四川菜。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xǐhuān chī guǎngdōng cài, zhìyú wǒ tàitài, tā xǐhuān chī sìchuān cài.
fields.translation: I like cantonese. as for my wife, she likes sichuanese.

fields.chinese: 毕业以后到底念研究生还是找工作,我还没考虑好。
fields.pinyin: Bìyè yǐhòu dàodǐ niàn yánjiūshēng háishì zhǎo gōngzuò, wǒ hái méi kǎolǜ hǎo.
fields.translation: Whether i really should go to graduate school or find a job after graduation, i still haven't thought it through.

fields.chinese: 小林毕业以后计划回中国工作,而不准备留在美国。
fields.pinyin: Xiǎo lín bìyè yǐhòu jìhuà huí zhōngguó gōngzuò, ér bù zhǔnbèi liú zài měiguó.
fields.translation: Xiao lin plans to go back to china to work, not to stay in the united states.

fields.chinese: 我哥哥已经拿到硕士学位, 而我才高中毕业。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ gēgē yǐjīng ná dào shuòshì xuéwèi, ér wǒ cái gāozhōng bìyè.
fields.translation: My older brother has already gotten his master's degree. i, on the other hand, have just graduated from high school.

fields.chinese: 我想拿双学位, 还得上四门课。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng ná shuāng xuéwèi, hái děi shàng sì mén kè.
fields.translation: I'd like to do a double major, so i still need four more classes.

fields.chinese: 下个学期我要选一门化学课, 另外再选两门电脑系的课,学分就够了。
fields.pinyin: Xià gè xuéqī wǒ yào xuǎn yī mén huàxué kè, lìngwài zài xuǎn liǎng mén diànnǎo xì de kè, xué fèn jiù gòule.
fields.translation: Next semester i'll take a chemistry course, plus two more computer science courses. then i'll have enough credits.

fields.chinese: 这个实习工作对化学系的学生来说,最合适不过了。
fields.pinyin: Zhège shíxí gōngzuò duì huàxué xì de xuéshēng lái shuō, zuì héshì bú guò le.
fields.translation: No internship is more appropriate for chemistry majors than this one.

fields.chinese: 小王实际上学分已经够了, 但他还想选两门电脑课, 明年春天再毕业。
fields.pinyin: Xiǎo wáng shíjìshang xuéfēn yǐjīng gòule, dàn tā hái xiǎng xuǎn liǎng mén diànnǎo kè, míngnián chūntiān zài bìyè.
fields.translation: Little wang actually has enough credits already, but he wants to take two more courses in computer science. he will graduate next spring.

fields.chinese: 下个学期我要选一门化学课, 另外再选两门电脑系的课,学分就够了。
fields.pinyin: Xià gè xuéqī wǒ yào xuǎn yī mén huàxué kè, lìngwài zài xuǎn liǎng mén diànnǎo xì de kè, xué fèn jiù gòule.
fields.translation: Next semester i'll take a chemistry course, plus two more computer science courses. then i'll have enough credits.

fields.chinese: 这个问题我们讨论来讨论去,最后还是没有办法解决。
fields.pinyin: Zhège wèntí wǒmen tǎolùn lái tǎolùn qù, zuìhòu háishì méiyǒu bànfǎ jiějué.
fields.translation: We discussed this problem again and again. in the end we still couldn't find a way to solve it.

fields.chinese: 把你的问题说出来,我们大家帮你解决。
fields.pinyin: Bǎ nǐ de wèntí shuō chūlái, wǒmen dàjiā bāng nǐ jiějué.
fields.translation: Tell us your problem; get it out in the open. we will help you solve it.

fields.chinese: 你要么学医，要么学经济，就是不能学文学。
fields.pinyin: Nǐ yàome xué yī, yàome xué jīngjì, jiùshì bùnéng xué wénxué.
fields.translation: You have to study either medicine or economics. it just can't be literature.

fields.chinese: 我想念研究生，要么上工学院，要么上管理学院，我还没跟指导教授谈。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng niàn yánjiūshēng, yàome shàng gōng xuéyuàn, yàome shàng guǎnlǐ xuéyuàn, wǒ hái méi gēn zhǐdǎo jiàoshòu tán.
fields.translation: I'd like to go to graduate school, either engineering or business school. i haven't discussed it yet with my advisor.

fields.chinese: 我想念研究生, 要么上工学院, 要么上管理学院, 我还没跟指导教授谈。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng niàn yánjiūshēng, yàome shàng gōng xuéyuàn, yàome shàng guǎnlǐ xuéyuàn, wǒ hái méi gēn zhǐdǎo jiàoshòu tán.
fields.translation: I'd like to go to graduate school, either engineering or business school. i haven't discussed it yet with my advisor.

fields.chinese: 我想念研究生, 要么上工学院, 要么上管理学院, 我还没跟指导教授谈。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng niàn yánjiūshēng, yàome shàng gōng xuéyuàn, yàome shàng guǎnlǐ xuéyuàn, wǒ hái méi gēn zhǐdǎo jiàoshòu tán.
fields.translation: I'd like to go to graduate school, either engineering or business school. i haven't discussed it yet with my advisor.

fields.chinese: 我想念研究生, 要么上工学院, 要么上管理学院, 我还没跟指导教授谈。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng niàn yánjiūshēng, yàome shàng gōng xuéyuàn, yàome shàng guǎnlǐ xuéyuàn, wǒ hái méi gēn zhǐdǎo jiàoshòu tán.
fields.translation: I'd like to go to graduate school, either engineering or business school. i haven't discussed it yet with my advisor.

fields.chinese: 你要么学医, 要么学经济, 就是不能学文学。
fields.pinyin: Nǐ yàome xué yī, yàome xué jīngjì, jiùshì bùnéng xué wénxué.
fields.translation: You have to study either medicine or economics. it just can't be literature.

fields.chinese: 学医呢, 没有意思, 学文学呢, 怕以后不好找工作。
fields.pinyin: Xué yī ne, méiyǒu yìsi, xué wénxué ne, pà yǐhòu buhǎo zhǎo gōngzuò.
fields.translation: Studying medicine, on the one hand, is boring. i'm worried that if i study literature, on the other hand, i won't be able to find a job.

fields.chinese: 可是我妈妈说, 学文科将来找工作不容易, 而且赚钱也少, 她希望我念金融。
fields.pinyin: Kěshì wǒ māmā shuō, xué wénkē jiānglái zhǎo gōngzuò bù róngyì, érqiě zhuàn qián yě shǎo, tā xīwàng wǒ niàn jīnróng.
fields.translation: But my mom says it's difficult to find a job if i study the humanities. besides, i won't make much money. she hopes that i will study finance.

fields.chinese: 我想学化学专业,将来好找工作。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng xué huàxué zhuānyè, jiānglái hǎo zhǎo gōngzuò.
fields.translation: I'd like to major in chemistry so that i can get a job easily.

fields.chinese: 可是我妈妈说, 学文科将来找工作不容易, 而且赚钱也少, 她希望我念金融。
fields.pinyin: Kěshì wǒ māmā shuō, xué wénkē jiānglái zhǎo gōngzuò bù róngyì, érqiě zhuàn qián yě shǎo, tā xīwàng wǒ niàn jīnróng.
fields.translation: But my mom says it's difficult to find a job if i study the humanities. besides, i won't make much money. she hopes that i will study finance.

fields.chinese: 加州冬天不冷，夏天不热，春天和秋天更舒服。
fields.pinyin: Jiāzhōu dōngtiān bù lěng, xiàtiān bù rè, chūntiān hé qiūtiān gèng shūfú.
fields.translation: California is not cold in winter, not hot in summer, spring and autumn are more comfortable.
Autumn is the harvest season.

fields.chinese: 加州冬天不冷，夏天不热，春天和秋天更舒服。
fields.pinyin: Jiāzhōu dōngtiān bù lěng, xiàtiān bù rè, chūntiān hé qiūtiān gèng shūfú.
fields.translation: California is not cold in winter, not hot in summer, spring and autumn are more comfortable.

fields.chinese: 小王觉得不舒服，今天不会来滑冰了。
fields.pinyin: Xiǎo wáng juédé bú shūfú, jīntiān bù huì lái huábīngle.
fields.translation: Xiao wang feels uncomfortable and won't come skating today.

fields.pinyin: Nǐ xiǎng bu xiǎng kàn zhōngguó diànyǐng?
fields.translation: Do you feel like going to see a chinese movie?

fields.chinese: 白老师觉得看英文书很有意思。
fields.pinyin: Bái lǎoshī juéde kàn  yīngwén shū hěn yǒu yìsi.
fields.translation: Teacher bai thinks reading english books is really fun.

fields.pinyin: Zhè ge zhōumò wǒ xiǎng kàn diànshì.
fields.translation: I want to watch television this weekend.

fields.pinyin: Nǐ xǐhuan bu xǐhuan kàn diànshì?
fields.translation: Do you like to watch television?

fields.chinese: 这些虽然都是小事儿，但是叫我非常生气。
fields.pinyin: Zhèxiē suīrán dōu shì xiǎoshì er, dànshì jiào wǒ fēicháng shēngqì.
fields.translation: These were all small matters, but they made me really upset.

fields.chinese: 别生气了，柯林也常常这样，一看球赛就什么事儿都忘了。
fields.pinyin: Bié shēngqìle, kē lín yě chángcháng zhèyàng, yī kàn qiúsài jiù shénme shì er dōu wàngle.
fields.translation: Don't be upset anymore. ke lin is often like that, too. whenever he starts watching a  ball game, he forgets about everything else.

fields.pinyin: Hái yǒu gèng jiào rén shēngqì de ne.
fields.translation: There was something even more maddening.
But they make me really upset.

fields.chinese: 上个星期六我要他陪我去看电影，他很高兴地答应了。
fields.pinyin: Shàng gè xīngqíliù wǒ yào tā péi wǒ qù kàn diànyǐng, tā hěn gāoxìng de dāyìngle.
fields.translation: Last saturday i wanted him to go with me to the movies. he happily agreed.

fields.chinese: 看见了我，妹妹很高兴地问：＂姐姐，你陪我看碟，好吗？”
fields.pinyin: Kànjiànle wǒ, mèimei hěn gāoxìng de wèn:"jiějiě, nǐ péi wǒ kàn dié, hǎo ma? ”
fields.translation: When she saw me, m y sister gladly asked, "older sister, watch the dvd with me, ok?

fields.chinese: 他很高兴地答应了，可是八点的电影，我等到八点一刻他还没到。
fields.pinyin: Tā hěn gāoxìng de dāyìngle, kěshì bā diǎn de diànyǐng, wǒ děngdào bā diǎn yī kè tā hái méi dào.
fields.translation: He happily agreed. the film was at 8:00. i waited till 8:15. he still hadn't arrived.

fields.pinyin: Dāyìng de shì yào zuò dào.
fields.translation: One should keep their promises.

fields.chinese: 打他手机，才知道他跑到另一家电影院去了。
fields.pinyin: Dǎ tā shǒujī, cái zhīdào tā pǎo dào lìng yījiā diànyǐngyuàn qùle.
fields.translation: I called his cell phone. only then did i find out that he had gone to another cinema.
What movie is showing in the movie theater?
I wish i could just break up with him.

fields.chinese: 难怪这两天他心情不好，原来他女朋友跟他吹了。
fields.pinyin: Nánguài zhè liǎng tiān tā xīnqíng bù hǎo, yuánlái tā nǚ péngyǒu gēn tā chuīle.
fields.translation: No wonder he's been in a bad mood the last couple of days. as it turns out, his girlfriend broke up with him.
Oh, so that's what happened.
Oh, i see.

fields.chinese: 房间里热得很，原来窗户没开。
fields.pinyin: Fángjiān lǐ rè dé hěn, yuánlái chuānghù méi kāi.
fields.translation: Oh, so that's what happened.

fields.chinese: 你还住在原来的宿舍吗？
fields.pinyin: Nǐ hái zhù zài yuánlái de sùshè ma?
fields.translation: Are you still living in the same dorm where you used to live in?

fields.chinese: 人们常说的交朋友，其实是谈恋爱的意思。
fields.pinyin: Rénmen cháng shuō de jiāo péngyǒu, qíshí shì tán liàn'ài de yìsi.
fields.translation: The "friend-making" people often talk about actually means dating.

fields.pinyin: Wǒ xiǎng hé nǐ jiāo gè péngyǒu.
fields.translation: I want to make friends with you.

fields.chinese: 他一会儿忘了我的生日，一会儿找不到钥匙。
fields.pinyin: Tā yīhuǐ'er wàngle wǒ de shēngrì, yīhuǐ'er zhǎo bù dào yàoshi.
fields.translation: One minute he forgets my birthday, the next he can't find his keys.

fields.chinese: 如果钥匙丢了，就得找他们帮忙。
fields.pinyin: Rúguǒ yàoshi diūle, jiù dé zhǎo tāmen bāngmáng.
fields.translation: If you lose the key, you have to ask them for help.

fields.chinese: 我哥哥经常丢三落四的，我看有一天会把自己丢了。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ gēgē jīngcháng diūsānlàsì de, wǒ kàn yǒu yītiān huì bǎ zìjǐ diūle.
fields.translation: My older brother is such a scatterbrain. i wouldn't be surprised if he forgot who he is one day.

fields.chinese: 你这么丢三落四的，难怪你女朋友老生气。
fields.pinyin: Nǐ zhème diūsānlàsì de, nánguài nǐ nǚ péngyǒu lǎo shēngqì.
fields.translation: You're so forgetful and absentminded. no wonder your girlfriend is always angry with you.

fields.chinese: 很多人以为我同屋比我大，实际上我比她大多了。
fields.pinyin: Hěnduō rén yǐwéi wǒ tóng wū bǐ wǒ dà, shíjì shang wǒ bǐ tā dàduōle.
fields.translation: A lot of people think my roommate is older than i am. actually, i'm much older than she is.

fields.chinese: 我一直以为整天跟数字打交道没什么意思，实际上挺好玩儿的。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ yīzhí yǐwéi zhěng tiān gēn shùzì dǎjiāodào méishénme yìsi, shíjì shang tǐng hǎowán er de.
fields.translation: I always had a misconception that it was boring to handle numbers and figures all day long. in fact, it's quite fun.

fields.chinese: 如果有一天不吵了，说不定你们就真的会分手。
fields.pinyin: Rúguǒ yǒu yītiān bù chǎole, shuō bu dìng nǐmen jiù zhēn de huì fēnshǒu.
fields.translation: When you stop fighting, you may well go your separate ways.

fields.chinese: 他们俩到底为什么分手？没有人知道。
fields.pinyin: Tāmen liǎ dàodǐ wèishéme fēnshǒu? méiyǒu rén zhīdào.
fields.translation: What's the real reason those two broke up? no one knows.

fields.chinese: 如果有一天不吵了，说不定你们就真的会分手。
fields.pinyin: Rúguǒ yǒu yītiān bù chǎole, shuō bu dìng nǐmen jiù zhēn de huì fēnshǒu.
fields.translation: When you stop fighting, you may well go your separate ways.

fields.pinyin: Shuō bu dìng tā xīnqíng bù hǎo.
fields.translation: Maybe he is in a bad mood.

fields.chinese: 哎，这个天明，怎么这么马虎！
fields.pinyin: Āi, zhège tiānmíng, zěnme zhème mǎhǔ!
fields.translation: How could tianming be so careless?
Don't be careless in the exam!

fields.chinese: 难怪他不知道这件事，他根本不看报纸！
fields.pinyin: Nánguài tā bù zhīdào zhè jiàn shì, tā gēnběn bù kàn bàozhǐ!
fields.translation: No wonder he doesn't  know this—he doesn't read newspapers at all.

fields.chinese: 难怪他不申请念研究生，我刚知道他已经找到工作了。
fields.pinyin: Nánguài tā bù shēnqǐng niàn yánjiūshēng, wǒ gāng zhīdào tā yǐjīng zhǎodào gōngzuò le.
fields.translation: No wonder he is not applying to graduate school. i just found out that he has already found a job.

fields.chinese: 难怪这两天他心情不好，原来他女朋友跟他吹了。
fields.pinyin: Nánguài zhè liǎng tiān tā xīnqíng bù hǎo, yuánlái tā nǚ péngyǒu gēn tā chuīle.
fields.translation: No wonder he's been in a bad mood the last couple of days. as it turns out, his girlfriend broke up with him.
No wonder you're not happy.

fields.chinese: 后来他见到我，不停地给我道歉。
fields.pinyin: Hòulái tā jiàn dào wǒ, bù tíng de gěi wǒ dàoqiàn.
fields.translation: When he saw me later, he kept apologizing to me.

fields.chinese: 我不停地写作业，还是没写完。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ bù tíng de xiě zuòyè, háishì méi xiě wán.
fields.translation: I kept doing my homework, but i still didn't finish it.

fields.chinese: 后来他见到我，不停地给我道歉。
fields.pinyin: Hòulái tā jiàn dào wǒ, bù tíng de gěi wǒ dàoqiàn.
fields.translation: When he saw me later, he kept apologizing to me.

fields.chinese: 做错事不道歉会造成感情问题。
fields.pinyin: Zuò cuò shì bù dàoqiàn huì zàochéng gǎnqíng wèntí.
fields.translation: Not apologizing for wrongdoing can cause relationship problems.
Couples don't  hold grudges when they quarrel.

fields.chinese: 他很记仇，最好不要让他生气。
fields.pinyin: Tā hěn jìchóu, zuì hǎo bùyào ràng tā shēngqì.
fields.translation: He holds grudge, so it is best not to make him angry.
Couples don't  hold grudges when they quarrel.

fields.chinese: 我看你跟柯林两个人挺好的，也不怎么吵架。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ kàn nǐ gēn kē lín liǎng gèrén tǐng hǎo de, yě bù zě me chǎojià.
fields.translation: You and ke lin seem very good together. you don't seem to fight a lot.

fields.chinese: 中国有一句话：“小两口吵架不记仇。”
fields.pinyin: Zhōngguó yǒu yījù huà:“xiǎo liǎngkǒu chǎojià bù jìchóu. ”
fields.translation: There is a  chinese saying "couples don't hold grudges when they quarrel".

fields.chinese: 我看你跟柯林两个人挺好的，也不怎么吵架。
fields.pinyin: Wǒ kàn nǐ gēn kē lín liǎng gèrén tǐng hǎo de, yě bù zě me chǎojià.
fields.translation: You and ke lin seem very good together. you don't seem to fight a lot.

fields.chinese: 这让我觉得他对我还是真心的。
fields.pinyin: Zhè ràng wǒ juédé tā duì wǒ háishì zhēnxīn de.
fields.translation: This made me feel that he genuinely cared about me.
Their love for each other is genuine.
His attitude was very sincere.

fields.chinese: 道歉的态度要是不好，不会被接受。
fields.pinyin: Dàoqiàn de tàidù yàoshi bù hǎo, bù huì bèi jiēshòu.
fields.translation: If the attitude of one's apology is not good, it will not be accepted.

fields.chinese: 哈哈！如果有一天不吵了，说不定你们就真的会分手。
fields.pinyin: Hāha! rúguǒ yǒu yītiān bù chǎole, shuō bu dìng nǐmen jiù zhēn de huì fēnshǒu.
fields.translation: Haha, when you stop fighting, you may well go your separate ways.
Hahahahaha. . .
